---
name: Step Fails With Rollback
version: 1.0.0
---

# Step failure triggers rollback

```step name="setup" rollback="undo-setup"
echo "setup done"
```

```step name="migrate" rollback="undo-migrate"
echo "migrate done"
```

```step name="deploy"
echo "about to fail" && exit 1
```

```step name="verify"
echo "should not run"
```

```rollback name="undo-setup"
echo "rolling back setup"
```

```rollback name="undo-migrate"
echo "rolling back migrate"
```
